channel.title: Rsps development team - only read if interested@
channel.description:
First I'd like to start by saying, I am sorry if this is the wrong place to post this; If it is please correct me! I am looking for a dedicated and small RSPS development and coding team that wants to make a nice server. I want it to be a 2006 or 317 based server with none of that 600+ shit, but if you guys want that, I can deal with it! I have not much java knowledge(lets say 6 months -still novice and learning) I have to say, the classes I'm taking are catching me up! We will decide on base when we get a chance to talk. You can keep the donations and I will pay you if I have too. I was looking for around a 3-4 person team. Some things I wanted to add are
-Quest that unlock features(like Rune Mysteries) -Runescape Quest -Members only features -Runescape eco system -Tutorial Island -All skills achievable We will discuss more when we figure this out! -pm me if interested or post skype/msn below
